race.comment: BALLON D'OR (1) has been racing in tougher grade and this is the easiest assignment she has contested for a long while. Just missed here three back and on her home track gets chance to break through. MAMUNO (2) has run on hard last two starts to just miss, placing at each. Overdue for a win and looks tough to stop. PLATINUM DESTROYER (6) has been going well over further without winning and drawing wide gates. Back in trip for this and drawn for a soft run with cover. Should be winding up late. RED FEATHERS (9) hit the line hard to score maiden success last time. Fitter again and is another who will be charging late.
